OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fcoastal showers overnight, but
OL,7,Fbecoming generally dry inland with
OL,8,Fclear spells. Turning chilly with
OL,9,Fgrass frost developing in rural areas.
OL,10,FThe odd fog patch forming in the
OL,11,Flighter winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FMonday should start mostly
OL,14,Ffine with some sunshine. However,
OL,15,Fshowers will break out during the day,
OL,16,Fturning locally heavy and thundery.
OL,17,FFeeling less chilly than recently with
OL,18,Fgentle winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
