OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,6,Fbright start in the east then turning
OL,7,Fcloudy from the west on Tuesday with
OL,8,Fpatchy rain. Wet and windy on
OL,9,FWednesday. Sunshine and showers on
OL,10,FThursday. Temperatures rising slightly.
